---
nvalt: ! 'Finding Notes


  ⌘ L (Look up) - go to search/title area

  ⌘ J / ⌘K - move highlight up/down in search results

  Enter - select highlighted note / create note with current title

  Esc - clear current search

  ⇧ ⌘ V - paste clipboard as new note

  ⌘ 0 - show bookmarks


  Editing


  ^ ⌘ P - toggle preview window

  ⌘ [ / ⌘ ] - outdent / indent highlighted text

  ⇧ ⌘ D - bookmark current note'
